.workbuddy/

# User journal inputs
/日志/*.md
!/日志/.gitkeep

# Generated review outputs
/复盘/**/*.md
!/复盘/**/.gitkeep

# Private runtime context files
/关于我/*.md
!/关于我/README.md
!/关于我/.gitkeep
!/关于我/templates/
!/关于我/templates/*.template.md

# Dynamically generated topic-thinking library
/关于我/思考/

/关于我/Analysis/*.md
!/关于我/Analysis/.gitkeep
